20:38.946 --> 20:42.116
ALL RIGHT, THEY'RE ABOUT

20:38.946 --> 20:42.116
TO PRESENT THE MERCHANDISE.

20:49.123 --> 20:50.583
THEY'RE BRINGING IT OUT

20:49.123 --> 20:50.583
RIGHT NOW.

20:50.624 --> 20:52.376
YEAH.

20:52.418 --> 20:54.336
ALL RIGHT, SLIGHT PROBLEM.

20:55.588 --> 20:57.173
SMART.

20:57.215 --> 20:59.967
OKAY, ELIOT, GET THEM TO PROVE

20:57.215 --> 20:59.967
THAT IT'S NOT AN OLD RECORDING.

21:00.009 --> 21:01.219
I'LL TRACE THE SIGNAL.

21:01.260 --> 21:03.096
UH, PARDON ME.

21:01.260 --> 21:03.096
I'M SOR--

21:03.137 --> 21:04.346
AM I THE ONLY ONE THAT --

21:04.388 --> 21:05.848
HOW DO WE KNOW

21:04.388 --> 21:05.848
THAT THIS IS NOT A RECORDING?

21:05.890 --> 21:07.016
COULD YOU ASK HIM TO MOVE IT?

21:07.058 --> 21:09.393
RESITUATE THE EGG.

21:13.856 --> 21:15.649
Okay, now, worst-case scenario,

21:15.691 --> 21:18.861
THAT ROOM YOU'RE LOOKING AT

21:15.691 --> 21:18.861
IS 100 MILES AWAY.

21:18.903 --> 21:21.197
I AM CHECKING

21:18.903 --> 21:21.197
THE INTERNET TRAFFIC

21:21.239 --> 21:22.865
IN AND OUT

21:21.239 --> 21:22.865
OF THE EMBASSY NETWORK.

21:22.907 --> 21:24.450
JUST GET ME

21:22.907 --> 21:24.450
A FEW MORE SECONDS.

21:24.491 --> 21:26.119
EXCUSE ME.

21:26.160 --> 21:27.327
CAN -- CAN YOU HAVE HIM SHOW ME

21:27.369 --> 21:31.373
A FIVE, THREE, FIVE,

21:27.369 --> 21:31.373
TWO, TWO, PLEASE?

21:31.415 --> 21:34.460
SHOW US FIVE, THREE, FIVE,

21:31.415 --> 21:34.460
TWO, TWO.

21:40.216 --> 21:42.384
YOU'RE OUT OF TIME, HARDISON.

21:42.426 --> 21:44.470
Look, nothing coming out

21:42.426 --> 21:44.470
of the embassy pipeline

21:44.511 --> 21:45.972
IS BIG ENOUGH

21:44.511 --> 21:45.972
TO BE THAT CAMERA FEED.

21:46.013 --> 21:48.099
THAT ROOM

21:46.013 --> 21:48.099
IS INSIDE THE BUILDING.

21:48.141 --> 21:50.810
ELIOT, DO YOU SEE ANY WIRES

21:48.141 --> 21:50.810
RUNNING INTO THE LAPTOP?

21:50.851 --> 21:51.811
NO.

21:51.852 --> 21:53.395
Okay, that means

21:51.852 --> 21:53.395
they're running it

21:53.437 --> 21:55.439
OFF THEIR AD HOC

21:53.437 --> 21:55.439
WIRELESS NETWORK.

21:55.481 --> 21:58.400
ALL I HAVE TO DO IS ISOLATE

21:55.481 --> 21:58.400
THE CAMERA'S I.P. ADDRESS.

21:58.442 --> 22:00.236
SEE, ALL THE COLD-WAR EMBASSIES

22:00.278 --> 22:02.362
WERE HONEYCOMBED

22:00.278 --> 22:02.362
WITH SECRET CORRIDORS

22:02.404 --> 22:05.116
AND -- AND -- AND SECRET ROOMS

22:02.404 --> 22:05.116
FOR LISTENING POSTS,

22:05.158 --> 22:07.034
BUT NONE OF THEM

22:05.158 --> 22:07.034
ARE USED ANYMORE.

22:07.076 --> 22:11.080
PARKER, I'M SENDING YOU

22:07.076 --> 22:11.080
THE MAP RIGHT NOW.

22:11.122 --> 22:12.915
[ BEEP ]

22:11.122 --> 22:12.915
-JUST FOLLOW THE PING.

22:12.957 --> 22:14.125
THAT'S YOUR EGG ROOM.

22:14.167 --> 22:16.502
I GOT IT.

22:16.543 --> 22:18.545
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

22:21.381 --> 22:23.301
YOU KNOW, I'M SURE YOU KNOW

22:21.381 --> 22:23.301
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

22:23.342 --> 22:25.303
I KNOW EXACTLY WHAT YOU MEAN --

22:23.342 --> 22:25.303
WHAT YOU MEAN.

22:25.343 --> 22:27.221
SORRY TO INTERRUPT THIS.

22:27.263 --> 22:29.556
[ STAMMERING ]

22:27.263 --> 22:29.556
CAN I GET TWO MINUTES?

22:29.598 --> 22:31.017
OH, SURE.

22:31.058 --> 22:32.852
-BYE.

22:32.893 --> 22:35.313
YEAH, ALEXANDER SEEMS,

22:32.893 --> 22:35.313
UH, NICE.

22:35.353 --> 22:39.108
YEAH, HE IS.

22:35.353 --> 22:39.108
AND TARA SEEMS SO SWEET.

22:39.150 --> 22:40.651
SHE'S A FOREIGN AID WORKER.

22:40.693 --> 22:42.695
REALLY?

22:40.693 --> 22:42.695
I MEAN, REALLY.

22:42.736 --> 22:45.031
YES. REALLY.

22:45.072 --> 22:47.241
SO, WHAT HAPPENED TO SOPHIE?

22:47.283 --> 22:49.910
THAT GOT A BIT COMPLICATED.

22:49.952 --> 22:51.912
RIGHT, BECAUSE

22:49.952 --> 22:51.912
YOU'RE SUCH A SIMPLE MAN.

22:51.954 --> 22:54.707
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

22:54.748 --> 22:56.834
ANYWAY, I SHOULD

22:54.748 --> 22:56.834
GO FIND ALEXANDER.

22:56.876 --> 22:59.337
YEAH. YOU KNOW, I'D ACTUALLY

22:56.876 --> 22:59.337
LIKE TO TALK TO HIM, TOO.

22:59.377 --> 23:01.505
YOU KNOW,

22:59.377 --> 23:01.505
MAYBE WE CAN GO TOGETHER,

23:01.547 --> 23:05.551
SEE WHAT HE'S UP TO...TOGETHER.

23:09.055 --> 23:10.931
[ SIGHS ]

23:09.055 --> 23:10.931
I'M RIGHT OUTSIDE THE DOOR.

23:10.973 --> 23:12.933
THERE'S NO SIGN

23:10.973 --> 23:12.933
OF ALEXANDER DOWN HERE.

23:14.310 --> 23:16.062
YOUR BIDS, PLEASE.

23:16.103 --> 23:18.605
ALL RIGHT, PARKER,

23:18.647 --> 23:21.567
THEY JUST SHUT OFF THE FEED

23:18.647 --> 23:21.567
TO THE EGG ROOM, OKAY?

23:21.608 --> 23:25.279
WHOEVER'S IN THAT ROOM

23:21.608 --> 23:25.279
IS GONNA BE COMING OUT.

23:25.321 --> 23:26.364
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:30.534 --> 23:31.869
[ SIGHS ]

23:31.911 --> 23:33.495
I can't get past him.

23:33.537 --> 23:35.622
I'M OUT OF POSITION.

23:37.791 --> 23:39.835
ME TOO.

23:41.379 --> 23:43.421
[ COUGHS ]

23:43.463 --> 23:46.217
OH.

23:46.259 --> 23:47.676
OOH.

23:47.718 --> 23:48.928
[ BOTTLE CLINKS ]

23:48.969 --> 23:51.389
HEY. WHOA,

23:48.969 --> 23:51.389
HO, HO, HO!

23:51.429 --> 23:53.307
WHAT ARE YOU DOING THERE, BUDDY?

23:51.429 --> 23:53.307
COME ON.

23:53.349 --> 23:54.934
[ Slurring ]

23:53.349 --> 23:54.934
YOU ARE INTERFERING

23:54.975 --> 23:59.646
WITH THE NATURAL COURSE

23:54.975 --> 23:59.646
OF MY EVENTS.

23:59.688 --> 24:00.647
LISTEN...

24:00.689 --> 24:03.567
UM, MAYBE YOU CAN HELP ME.

24:03.609 --> 24:06.279
I'M SUPPOSED TO MEET

24:03.609 --> 24:06.279
MY BROTHER'S --

24:06.320 --> 24:08.822
IT'S A SECRET.

24:08.864 --> 24:10.490
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

24:10.532 --> 24:11.742
CAN YOU HELP?

24:11.784 --> 24:13.244
YEAH, ABSOLUTELY.

24:13.286 --> 24:14.536
-COOL.

24:13.286 --> 24:14.536
-YOU COME WITH ME.

24:14.578 --> 24:16.080
-AND GET MY BOTTLE.

24:14.578 --> 24:16.080
-IT'S EMPTY.

24:16.122 --> 24:17.581
-OKAY. YOU SURE?

24:16.122 --> 24:17.581
-I'LL GET RID OF IT FOR YOU.

24:17.623 --> 24:19.375
-YOU'RE VERY STRONG.

24:17.623 --> 24:19.375
-THANK YOU.

24:19.417 --> 24:20.500
OH. CAREFUL NOW.

24:26.382 --> 24:29.385
[ SIGHS ]

24:26.382 --> 24:29.385
I'VE GOT THE PACKAGE.

24:29.427 --> 24:31.887
GREAT. LET'S CLEAR OUT BEFORE

24:29.427 --> 24:31.887
THEY REALIZE THE EGG IS GONE.

24:31.929 --> 24:33.097
ANYONE SEEN NATE?

24:35.433 --> 24:36.934
YOU'RE WELCOME.

24:36.976 --> 24:39.103
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU PEOPLE

24:36.976 --> 24:39.103
EVER MANAGE --

24:39.145 --> 24:40.354
[ FEEDBACK ]

24:40.396 --> 24:42.022
OH, I'M SORRY, MAN.

24:42.064 --> 24:44.150
THAT JUST HAPPENS SOMETIMES

24:42.064 --> 24:44.150
WITH THE EAR BUDS --

24:44.191 --> 24:45.318
YOU KNOW, FEEDBACK.

24:45.359 --> 24:46.902
[ SIGHS ]

24:46.944 --> 24:49.029
AS I WAS SAYING, THE METHOD --

24:49.071 --> 24:50.406
[ FEEDBACK ]

24:50.448 --> 24:51.740
SORRY.

24:53.451 --> 24:55.453
THIS ISN'T GONNA STOP UNTIL I --

24:55.493 --> 24:56.494
[ FEEDBACK ]

24:56.536 --> 24:59.332
STOP TALKING.

24:56.536 --> 24:59.332
SHH. PLEASE.

25:06.213 --> 25:09.175
WHERE'S NATE?

25:09.216 --> 25:11.760
I SWEAR I SAW HIM DUCK IN HERE.

25:11.802 --> 25:15.722
YES, BUT WE HAVEN'T CHECKED

25:11.802 --> 25:15.722
THE SOUTHEAST CORRIDOR,

25:15.764 --> 25:16.932
AND, YOU KNOW, I'D REALLY LIKE

25:16.974 --> 25:19.185
TO GIVE HIM

25:16.974 --> 25:19.185
THE GOOD NEWS MYSELF.

25:19.226 --> 25:20.811
I'VE HEARD THAT VOICE BEFORE.

25:20.853 --> 25:22.646
WHAT?

25:22.688 --> 25:24.690
HUH?

25:24.731 --> 25:25.941
HMM?

25:25.983 --> 25:27.485
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW

25:25.983 --> 25:27.485
THAT YOU DO IT, DO YOU?

25:27.525 --> 25:30.321
I'M SORRY, DOING WHAT?

25:30.363 --> 25:32.490
-THAT'S YOUR INTERCOM VOICE.

25:30.363 --> 25:32.490
-MAGGIE, LISTEN --

25:32.530 --> 25:33.699
YOU LIED TO ME!

25:33.740 --> 25:34.867
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

25:34.908 --> 25:36.369
MAGGIE, ALEXANDER --

25:34.908 --> 25:36.369
YOU NEED TO KNOW --

25:36.410 --> 25:37.495
DO  NOT  DRAG HIM INTO THIS.

25:37.535 --> 25:38.996
WELL, HE'S ALREADY INTO THIS,

25:39.038 --> 25:40.956
OKAY, MORE THAN YOU -- I HATE

25:39.038 --> 25:40.956
TO BE THE ONE TO TELL YOU.

25:40.998 --> 25:42.249
NATE!

25:42.291 --> 25:43.292
-NO!

25:42.291 --> 25:43.292
[ TASER CRACKLES ]

26:01.185 --> 26:02.269
[ GASPS ]

26:02.311 --> 26:03.603
WHAT?

26:03.645 --> 26:06.232
NO OFFENSE, BUT I THINK

26:03.645 --> 26:06.232
I WAS BETTER OFF IN JAIL.

26:06.273 --> 26:07.233
[ GROANS ]

26:07.274 --> 26:08.359
OH.

26:08.401 --> 26:10.486
I THINK WE WERE TASERED --

26:10.528 --> 26:12.988
SAME THING THAT HAPPENED TO ME

26:10.528 --> 26:12.988
AT THE ROBBERY.

26:13.030 --> 26:14.156
AH.

26:14.198 --> 26:18.618
DID...YOU SEE WHO DID THIS?

26:18.660 --> 26:20.413
YEAH, THEY LOOKED LIKE

26:18.660 --> 26:20.413
SECURITY GUARDS

26:20.454 --> 26:21.455
FROM THE EMBASSY.

26:21.497 --> 26:24.542
YEAH, ELIOT WARNED ME

26:21.497 --> 26:24.542
ABOUT THAT.

26:24.582 --> 26:26.584
I ALREADY TRIED IT.

26:24.582 --> 26:26.584
IT'S LOCKED.

26:26.626 --> 26:27.711
[ BANGING ]

26:26.626 --> 26:27.711
-COME ON, COME ON.

26:27.753 --> 26:30.005
UHH!

26:30.047 --> 26:31.631
I JUST SAID IT WAS LOCKED.

26:31.673 --> 26:34.843
YEAH, NO, I KNOW.

26:31.673 --> 26:34.843
IT'S JUST, UH...

26:34.885 --> 26:37.054
MEN.

26:37.096 --> 26:39.348
[ SIGHS ]

26:42.393 --> 26:43.727
THIS ISN'T GOOD.

26:43.769 --> 26:45.896
I CAN'T GET HIM ON THE

26:43.769 --> 26:45.896
CELLPHONE, NOT ON THE COMM.

26:45.938 --> 26:47.773
CASE IS CLOSED, PEOPLE.

26:47.814 --> 26:49.024
THE EGG IS BACK.

26:49.066 --> 26:50.443
I'M SURE NATE

26:49.066 --> 26:50.443
IS BREAKING IT TO MAGGIE

26:50.484 --> 26:52.403
ABOUT HER CONTINUED

26:50.484 --> 26:52.403
POOR CHOICE IN MEN.

26:52.445 --> 26:54.530
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

26:52.445 --> 26:54.530
-IT'S NATE'S CELL.

26:54.572 --> 26:56.490
[ Distorted voice ]

26:54.572 --> 26:56.490
We have your people.

26:56.532 --> 26:57.657
No police.

26:57.699 --> 27:00.827
Await further instructions.

27:03.539 --> 27:04.915
[ BEEPING ]

27:03.539 --> 27:04.915
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

27:04.957 --> 27:07.126
CALLING THE POLICE.

27:04.957 --> 27:07.126
THEY DON'T GET TO DICTATE TO --

27:07.167 --> 27:09.878
WE'RE NOT CALLING THE COPS.

27:09.920 --> 27:12.756
TWO HOSTAGES MEANS THEY CAN

27:09.920 --> 27:12.756
KILL ONE TO MAKE A POINT.

27:12.798 --> 27:14.841
[ CELLPHONE CLATTERS ]

27:14.883 --> 27:16.218
ALL RIGHT, LISTEN.

27:16.260 --> 27:18.262
THERE'S THREE TYPES OF CALLS

27:16.260 --> 27:18.262
WE CAN GET NEXT.

27:18.304 --> 27:21.432
ONE -- AMATEUR.

27:18.304 --> 27:21.432
CASH AND A DUMP SITE.

27:21.474 --> 27:23.100
NUMBER TWO -- PROFESSIONAL.

27:23.142 --> 27:27.271
THAT'S WIRE TRANSFERS AND

27:23.142 --> 27:27.271
MULTIPLE-LOCATION DROP-OFFS.

27:27.313 --> 27:29.189
AND THREE -- TARGETED.

27:29.231 --> 27:30.316
TARGETED TOWARD US?

27:30.357 --> 27:31.775
NO.

27:31.817 --> 27:35.488
TOWARDS A SPECIFIC

27:31.817 --> 27:35.488
RANSOM DEMAND --

27:35.529 --> 27:36.863
NOT CASH.

27:36.905 --> 27:38.782
YOU'RE NOT RISKING

27:36.905 --> 27:38.782
A $9 MILLION ARTIFACT...

27:38.824 --> 27:41.535
-IT MIGHT BE THE ONLY CHANCE.

27:38.824 --> 27:41.535
-...ON A HUNCH!

27:41.577 --> 27:44.121
LET ME RUN THIS.

27:44.163 --> 27:46.165
WE TRACK THE CALLS,

27:44.163 --> 27:46.165
FIND OUT WHOEVER IT IS,

27:46.206 --> 27:47.291
HAVE THE POLICE SURROUND --

27:47.333 --> 27:50.127
STERLING,

27:47.333 --> 27:50.127
I'M THE RETRIEVAL SPECIALIST.

27:50.169 --> 27:52.087
THAT'S MY JOB.

27:54.047 --> 27:57.593
YOUR FRIENDS' LIVES

27:54.047 --> 27:57.593
HANG IN THE BALANCE,

27:57.635 --> 27:59.386
AND YOU'RE GONNA TAKE YOUR CUES

27:59.428 --> 28:02.764
OFF A PUNCH-UP ARTIST

27:59.428 --> 28:02.764
INSTEAD OF ME?

28:06.644 --> 28:08.937
CALL ME WHEN YOU NEED ME.

28:08.979 --> 28:11.398
'CAUSE YOU  WILL  NEED ME.

28:16.945 --> 28:18.696
ALL RIGHT, BASICALLY,

28:16.945 --> 28:18.696
WE'RE LOOKING FOR ANYTHING

28:18.738 --> 28:20.449
-TO HELP US GET OUT OF HERE.

28:18.738 --> 28:20.449
-NATE?

28:20.491 --> 28:22.618
AT THE PARTY,

28:20.491 --> 28:22.618
YOU WERE TRYING TO TELL ME

28:22.660 --> 28:23.869
SOMETHING ABOUT ALEXANDER.

28:23.910 --> 28:25.245
YEAH, WE CAN DEAL

28:23.910 --> 28:25.245
WITH THAT LATER.

28:25.287 --> 28:26.622
NO. WHY DON'T

28:25.287 --> 28:26.622
YOU JUST TELL ME NOW?

28:26.664 --> 28:28.248
NO, GETTING YOU OUT OF HERE

28:26.664 --> 28:28.248
IS THE MAIN PRIORITY.

28:28.290 --> 28:29.583
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME WHAT'S --

28:29.625 --> 28:32.002
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

28:29.625 --> 28:32.002
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS!

28:32.044 --> 28:33.920
I'LL GIVE YOU ANYTHING!

28:32.044 --> 28:33.920
TAKE MY WATCH!

28:33.962 --> 28:35.673
IT'S A PATEK PHILLIPE!

28:35.713 --> 28:36.965
OH, THANK GOD!

28:37.007 --> 28:39.801
IT'S ALEXANDER.

28:37.007 --> 28:39.801
HE'S GONE CRAZY.

28:41.261 --> 28:44.056
THAT'S WHAT I WAS TRYING

28:41.261 --> 28:44.056
TO TELL YOU UPSTAIRS.

28:46.350 --> 28:49.061
THERE'S NO SIGN OF ALEXANDER

28:46.350 --> 28:49.061
AT HIS HOME OR THE EMBASSY.

28:49.102 --> 28:50.979
AND HIS EMBASSY CAR

28:49.102 --> 28:50.979
HAS BEEN SIGNED OUT.

28:51.021 --> 28:51.980
HE'S SPOOKED.

28:52.022 --> 28:54.650
HE'S ANGRY.

28:52.022 --> 28:54.650
WE TOOK HIS PAYDAY.

28:54.692 --> 28:57.069
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

28:54.692 --> 28:57.069
-ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

29:00.239 --> 29:01.615
GO.

29:01.657 --> 29:04.201
[ Distorted voice ]

29:01.657 --> 29:04.201
If you follow our instructions,

29:04.243 --> 29:05.952
your friends

29:04.243 --> 29:05.952
will be returned unharmed.

29:05.994 --> 29:07.996
WE AGREE.

29:05.994 --> 29:07.996
TELL US WHAT YOU WANT.

29:08.038 --> 29:10.708
[ Normal voice ]

29:08.038 --> 29:10.708
You owe me $9 million.

29:10.749 --> 29:12.251
IT'S ALEX.

29:10.749 --> 29:12.251
IT'S ALEXANDER.

29:12.292 --> 29:14.336
I still have a buyer

29:12.292 --> 29:14.336
for the egg.

29:14.378 --> 29:16.589
RETURN IT,

29:14.378 --> 29:16.589
AND I RETURN YOUR FRIENDS.

29:16.630 --> 29:20.342
I WANT PROOF OF LIFE NOW.

29:20.384 --> 29:21.927
Agreed.

29:21.968 --> 29:23.220
[ GRUNTS ]

29:23.262 --> 29:25.639
YEAH, WE GOT

29:23.262 --> 29:25.639
ALEXANDER'S FINANCIALS,

29:25.681 --> 29:27.266
AND HE'S THREE MONTHS

29:25.681 --> 29:27.266
FROM BANKRUPTCY,

29:27.307 --> 29:29.560
AND THE THEFT WAS DEFINITELY

29:27.307 --> 29:29.560
AN INSIDE JOB.

29:29.602 --> 29:30.936
YOU KNOW,

29:29.602 --> 29:30.936
I THINK YOU WERE RIGHT.

29:30.977 --> 29:32.271
I DON'T THINK WE SHOULD

29:30.977 --> 29:32.271
TALK ABOUT THIS RIGHT NOW.

29:32.312 --> 29:33.772
LOOK, I-I KNOW IT IS DIFFICULT

29:33.813 --> 29:34.981
HEARING THIS

29:33.813 --> 29:34.981
ABOUT YOUR BOYFRIEND.

29:35.023 --> 29:36.149
I GET THAT.

29:36.191 --> 29:38.694
BOYFRIEND? WE DATE, NATE.

29:36.191 --> 29:38.694
WE GO ON DATES.

29:38.736 --> 29:40.153
I KNOW THAT'S PROBABLY

29:38.736 --> 29:40.153
NOT AS EXCITING

29:40.195 --> 29:42.072
AS STEALING ART

29:40.195 --> 29:42.072
WITH YOUR NEW FRIEND TARA.

29:42.114 --> 29:43.699
I'M NOT DATING TARA.

29:43.741 --> 29:45.075
NOW, WHAT YOU DO

29:43.741 --> 29:45.075
IS YOU MAKE A CUT HERE --

29:45.117 --> 29:46.744
I KNEW IT.

29:45.117 --> 29:46.744
YOU'RE DATING SOPHIE.

29:46.785 --> 29:48.370
[ SCOFFS ] I'M NOT

29:46.785 --> 29:48.370
DATING SOPHIE, EITHER.

29:48.412 --> 29:50.038
I'M NOT DATING ANYONE.

29:50.080 --> 29:52.124
BUT GOOD FOR YOU, MOVING ON

29:50.080 --> 29:52.124
WITH A THIEVING KIDNAPPER.

29:52.165 --> 29:53.208
THAT'S TERRIFIC.

29:53.250 --> 29:55.043
ALLEGED  THIEVING KIDNAPPER.

29:55.085 --> 29:57.212
-WELL, CALL IT --

29:55.085 --> 29:57.212
-NO, IT'S ALL TRUE.

29:57.254 --> 30:00.633
I FOUND SOME IRREGULARITIES

29:57.254 --> 30:00.633
IN MR. LUNDY'S FINANCES.

30:00.674 --> 30:03.343
HE TOLD ME THEY WERE NO PROBLEM.

30:00.674 --> 30:03.343
HE TOOK THE FILES,

30:03.385 --> 30:05.679
WHICH, OF COURSE,

30:03.385 --> 30:05.679
TIPPED ME OFF.

30:05.721 --> 30:07.889
-I KNEW SOMETHING WAS WRONG.

30:05.721 --> 30:07.889
-THERE'S OUR PROOF OF LIFE.

30:07.931 --> 30:09.349
I DIDN'T HAVE ACCESS

30:07.931 --> 30:09.349
TO ALL OF HIS BOOKS.

